Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: A Padawan served the Jedi Order and the Galactic Republic during the Dark Jedi Conflict, an event which took place in the Cularin system in 181 BBY.

A Force-sensitive was trained in the ways of the Force by the Jedi Order during the last millennia of the Galactic Republic. A student of the Coruscant Jedi Temple, the Jedi Initiate was selected by a a female Jedi Consular to train as a Padawan. Along with his master, the pair was dispatched by the Jedi High Council to bring an end to the Dark Jedi Conflict which had consumed the Cularin system in 181 BBY. Teaching the natives of the star system to fight and mobilize against the armies of the fallen Jedi Kibh Jeen, the Jedi pair were able to lure Jeen's warriors into a trap. During the battle, the Padawan and the Knight confronted Jeen and slew him, bringing his reign of terror to an end.
